##  Outcome
 -  *FIX-READY* (`$HOME/todo/DIFF-002`, stopped at commit boundary). ROOT CAUSE was
    NOT the sub-relay framing â€” it was *`graf/DIFFREF.c:451` `diffref_emit_gitlink`*,
    the one diff emitter that wrote the gitlink line `<path> <old>..<new>` via raw
    `fprintf(stdout,â€¦)`, bypassing the canonical `GRAFHunkEmit â†’ HUNKu8sFeedOut` channel.
    In `--tlv` that raw text LEADS the stream un-enveloped (before the `H` records);
    bro's `bro_drain_tlv` (`bro/BRO.c:2560` â†’ `dog/HUNK.c:187 HUNKu8sDrain â†’ TLVu8sDrain`)
